---
import { SkeletonPage, BasicPage } from '@layouts'
import { SEO } from '@components'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

const lang = { code: 'fr' }
---

<SkeletonPage {lang}>
  <SEO
    slot="head"
    ogType="website"
    title="Inauguration Wanna Play - 10 juin 2018"
    description="Retour sur l'événement fondateur de Wanna Play : l'invocation de Ruego."
    socialImage={'/archive/images/mailChimp_header-invitation-2.png'}
    ogVideo={false}
    twitterCard="summary"
  />

  <BasicPage {lang}>
    <main class="center max stack gap-down-h3" style="margin-top: 0;">
      <header class="stack gap-down-h4 center text">
        <Image
          src="/archive/images/mailChimp_header-invitation-2.png"
          alt="Inauguration"
          width={600}
          height={200}
          style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: var(--border-radius-m);"
        />
        <h1>
          <span class="color-primary">Inauguration</span><br />
          <span class="color-secondary">et soirée jeux</span>
        </h1>
        <p><strong>Dimanche 10 juin 2018 à 16h</strong></p>
      </header>

      <section class="stack gap-down-h4 center text padding-x-relative-l">
        <p>
          Il y a de ça un an maintenant, nous sommes partis en quête pour libérer les joueurs de
          leurs entraves. Aujourd'hui, plus que jamais, le mal nous menace mais la rébellion est en
          marche et l'espoir grandit tous les jours dans le cœur des vaillants résistants !
        </p>

        <div class="stack gap-down-h6">
          <h3>Inscris-toi !</h3>
          <p class="color-red">C'est obligatoire mais gratuit</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <section
        class="grid gap-h5 padding-h3 border-radius-m"
        data-c-p="teal"
        data-c-p-var="funky-contrast"
        style="--width-column: 130px; text-align: center;"
      >
        <div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">+110</p><p>joueurs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">11</p><p>partenaires</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">+70</p><p>jeux proposés</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">40</p><p>tables créées</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">16</p><p>interviews</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
            <p class="size-h1 stat-nb">8</p><p>jeux offerts (Asmodee)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Règles du jeu -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <div
          class="stack gap-down-h5 padding-h3 border-radius-l center text"
          data-c-p="teal"
          data-c-p-var="contrast"
        >
          <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-00.png" alt="" width="80" />
          <h2>Règles du jeu</h2>
        </div>

        <div
          class="cluster gap-h4 justify-content-center"
          style="--align-items: flex-start; text-align: center;"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h6" style="width: 120px;">
              <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-02.png" alt="" style="width: 80px; margin: auto;" />
              <p><strong>16h &gt; 22h</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h6" style="width: 120px;">
              <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-03.png" alt="" style="width: 80px; margin: auto;" />
              <p><strong>3 &gt; 99 ans</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h6" style="width: 120px;">
              <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-04.png" alt="" style="width: 80px; margin: auto;" />
              <p><strong>Coopératif</strong></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- But du jeu -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <h3>But du jeu</h3>
        <p>
          Le temps d'une soirée, nous célébrons <strong>Ruego, le jinn du jeu</strong>. Enchaîne les
          parties de tes jeux préférés pour attirer ses faveurs !
        </p>

        <h3>Déroulement de la "party"</h3>
        <p class="center text">
          Accueil des joueurs • Explication des règles • Organisation de tables • Et autres
          surprises…
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Phases de jeu -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <h3>Phases de jeu</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-h4" style="--width-column: 100px; text-align: center;">
          <div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
              <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-02.png" alt="" class="border-radius-s" style="width: 100%;" />
              <p>Un verre au bar</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
              <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-03.png" alt="" class="border-radius-s" style="width: 100%;" />
              <p>Grignotages</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
              <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-04.png" alt="" class="border-radius-s" style="width: 100%;" />
              <p>Rencontres</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h7">
              <img src="/archive/images/WP-MailChimp-invit-05.png" alt="" class="border-radius-s" style="width: 100%;" />
              <p>Jeux</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Mise en place -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <h3>Mise en place</h3>
        <div class="cluster gap-h4 justify-content-center" style="text-align: center;">
          <div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h6" style="width: 140px;">
              <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-08.png" alt="" width="80" style="margin: auto;" />
              <p>Dimanche <strong>10 juin</strong> 2018<br /><strong>16h</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="stack gap-down-h6" style="width: 140px;">
              <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-09.png" alt="" width="80" style="margin: auto;" />
              <p><strong>Espace Maurice Carême</strong><br />rue du Chapelain 1-7, Anderlecht</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Sur place (tilted card) -->
      <section class="sur-place-box box no-border padding-h4" data-c-p="teal" data-c-p-var="funky">
        <div class="stack gap-down-h5">
          <h3 class="color-secondary">Sur place</h3>
          <div class="grid gap-h5" style="--width-column: 70px; text-align: center; font-size: var(--size-h5);">
            <div>
              <div class="stack gap-down-h8">
                <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-10.png" alt="" style="width: 60px; margin: auto;" />
                <p>Garderie</p>
              </div>
              <div class="stack gap-down-h8">
                <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-12.png" alt="" style="width: 60px; margin: auto;" />
                <p>Accessibilité</p>
              </div>
              <div class="stack gap-down-h8">
                <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-11.png" alt="" style="width: 60px; margin: auto;" />
                <p>Terrasse</p>
              </div>
              <div class="stack gap-down-h8">
                <img src="/archive/images/icone-invit-mailing-13.png" alt="" style="width: 60px; margin: auto;" />
                <p>WC</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Partenaires -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <div class="center" style="max-width: 500px;">
          <img src="/archive/images/mailChimp_header-partenaires.png" alt="Partenaires" style="width: 100%;" />
        </div>

        <!-- Partenaires principaux -->
        <div class="cluster gap-h4 justify-content-center" style="--align-items: center;">
          <div>
            <img src="/archive/images/ASMODEE.png" alt="Asmodee" style="height: 100px; object-fit: contain;" />
            <img src="/archive/images/espace-careme.jpg" alt="Espace Carême" style="height: 100px; object-fit: contain;" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Autres partenaires -->
        <div class="cluster gap-h5 justify-content-center" style="--align-items: center;">
          <div>
            <img src="/archive/images/Ludivine.png" alt="Ludivine" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/casse-noisettes.png" alt="Casse-Noisettes" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/lets-play-together.png" alt="Let's Play Together" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/the-cookie-tree.jpg" alt="The Cookie Tree" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/jeux-spellen-1082.png" alt="Jeux Spellen" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/Geek-Attitude-Games-01.png" alt="GAG" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/jeuxsticiers.png" alt="Jeuxsticiers" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/ace_workshops.png" alt="Ace Workshops" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/ReposProduction.png" alt="Repos Production" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/de-joueur.png" alt="De Joueur" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/govinda-box.png" alt="Govinda" class="partner-logo" />
            <img src="/archive/images/Des-jeux-une-fois.png" alt="Des jeux une fois" class="partner-logo" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Vidéo -->
      <section class="stack gap-down-h4">
        <h3>Souvenirs en vidéo</h3>
        <iframe
          width="100%"
          height="315"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/laySniWhIU4"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </section>
    </main>
  </BasicPage>
</SkeletonPage>

<style>
  /* Tilted "sur place" card */
  .sur-place-box {
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
    margin: var(--size-h3) auto;
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 600px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-raised-s);
  }

  /* Stat numbers — use color-primary from palette */
  .stat-nb {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Color helpers not in the global system */
  .color-primary { color: var(--color-primary); }
  .color-secondary { color: var(--color-secondary); }
  .color-red { color: var(--color-red); }

  /* Partner logos */
  .partner-logo {
    height: 70px;
    width: 70px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
</style>
